enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require the conversion of a Date object to a Calendar object using the same TimeZone.
The validate method can be used to convert a String to a Date object, which can then be used as input for compareWeeks.
compareDates should be invoked before compareWeeks if the test scenario involves comparing dates before weeks.
compareMonths should be invoked before compareWeeks if the test scenario involves comparing months before weeks.
